{"tid":2361016,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"祭壇守護者打游擊悼念","createTime":"2021-01-10T09:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T10:21:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a717383717068ae7480418eb4598e0b26910b38b","tid":2361016,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/6UZIQHPV2NBXBHDZZYB55M5OBY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2F6UZIQHPV2NBXBHDZZYB55M5OBY%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7Q3kfWbBCvxMfTTNG0K1D1Y%3D&h=5aff850c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2F6UZIQHPV2NBXBHDZZYB55M5OBY%2F&h=b8ce104f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/6UZIQHPV2NBXBHDZZYB55M5OBY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n祭壇守護者打游擊悼念<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「尚十祭壇」被消失，。。。。。。。。。。過去一年，她在小小一個停車場內，見證着港人自由萎縮。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞： 手足：車場油漆蓋不住思念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IepvUscugYz-CjGsTrSwqw8rmN4=/1460x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/32WVW6CGPFBP5F4RV34ZEELULU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIepvUscugYz-CjGsTrSwqw8rmN4%3D%2F1460x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F32WVW6CGPFBP5F4RV34ZEELULU.jpg&h=f76f8441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■阿儀每日堅持到尚德停車場，為梓樂守住燭光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每日風雨不改點蠟燭<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳街坊阿儀自言14個月前仍是「港豬」一名，直至22歲的周梓樂從她成長的地方失去性命，令她改變並化身成祭壇的守護者，每日風雨不改一放工便往打理祭壇。她觀察到蠟燭約三小時便會燒盡，於是校好鬧鐘，每隔三小時落樓燃點，只為兌現一句承諾&mdash;&mdash;「『彥梓路』交畀我哋將軍將街坊，梓樂一定會有點燭光喺度。」她更與街坊將祭壇對出的唐明街改名「彥梓路」，期望彥霖及梓樂能夠如燕子般在天上自由飛翔。<br />\n<br />\n阿儀憶述，祭壇最初是兩個大圓形，去年初被警方以夾斗車清走，後來街坊重建成三角形祭壇，隨即又被清空。之後發生大圍捕，警方又以限聚令趕人，慢慢街坊不敢公開悼念。每路經此處，她的內心盡是欷歔，「以前全部都係文宣，成個壆都係蠟燭，𠵱家冇晒，唯一一樣嘢多咗就係閉路電視。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：有緣街坊首響應呼籲出庭  是證人也是守護者「悲劇中找些好事」<br />\n<br />\n無法重建祭壇，阿儀堅持為梓樂守住一點燭光，每晚都跟警察及保安打游擊，「我會袋定幾粒蠟燭，幾個杯仔，圍繞住停車場搵個位點」，每當點燃蠟燭後，她會把握時間播幾首歌便離去，因為15分鐘後便有保安到場。<br />\n<br />\n她笑言已被盯上，更曾因點燃蠟燭被控亂拋垃圾罰款1,500元：「貼嘢佢會告你刑毀，但擺地下佢最多告你掉垃圾，所以我盡量唔黐牆，擺地下。」<br />\n<br />\n家人及街坊曾勸她別再冒險，她亦深明一點燭光並無實際作用，但對於一位大好青年無辜喪命，她就是放不低：「唔可以就咁算，我唔服呀！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JeKqfWNJ08eq-jECgCHeMGL8oIU=/1536x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IBOD4PZXNNBNBGZB74233FUVDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJeKqfWNJ08eq-jECgCHeMGL8oIU%3D%2F1536x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIBOD4PZXNNBNBGZB74233FUVDA.jpg&h=2bda6741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周梓樂及陳彥霖的死，觸動市民心靈。"},{"pid":"b1513ab3ecd61237f406e1a87567bb691eade34f","tid":2361016,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T09:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22aaa8123400c8c4ae0e66a9e4520d444e1d155a","tid":2361016,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}